      "description": "Offering an exceptional 2004 BMW M3 (E46) finished in Carbon Black. This collector-grade example features the S54B32 inline-six, renowned for its 8,000 RPM redline and high-pressure Double VANOS variable valve timing. Power is delivered via a 6-speed Getrag manual gearbox to a variable M-differential lock, ensuring mechanical grip and telepathic feedback. The chassis is structurally perfect, with a proactively reinforced rear subframe and fresh bushings throughout the multi-link rear suspension. The Individual Throttle Bodies (ITBs) are perfectly synced, providing crisp induction notes and immediate throttle response. This is a zero-compromise, analog driver\u2019s car with flawless factory paint and a pristine Nappa leather interior.",
